data.description: Welcome to your spacious 6-bedroom, 4 full bath home with FULL finished in-law suite basement complete with private entrance and covered patio!  Guest suite on the main level and lovely 4-season porch!  Nestled in the highly desired BROOKWOOD school district and gorgeous River Oak Hills subdivision with no HOA fees!  Additional features include two brand NEW HVAC systems, NEW high-end stainless appliances, whole house water filtration/softener system, nearly NEW luxury carpet and pad upstairs, upgraded light fixtures, bidets, fiber optic internet and more!  Bright, open granite and stainless kitchen complete with new appliances, beautiful breakfast area, abundant cabinetry, coffee bar area, walk-in pantry – all with views to beautiful back yard and extended deck, family room and sunroom!  Spacious, fireside family room perfect for cozy evenings!  Amazing 4-season sunroom is the PERFECT spot for your morning coffee!  Second floor boasts new luxury carpeting, 4 additional bedrooms plus bonus room!  Owner’s suite features huge walk-in closet, whirlpool tub and oversized shower!  Fabulous daylight basement featuring bedroom, kitchen and dining area, living room, full bath, covered patio and its own exterior entry – perfect for guests or in-laws!  SO many outdoor entertaining areas including covered front porch, side “friendship” porch, huge back deck with lounging area, grilling area, dining space and firepit seating area plus private, beautifully landscaped back yard!   Convenient to award winning Brookwood schools, excellent shopping, dining, entertainment and easy access to Ronald Regan Hwy, I-85 and all that Atlanta has to offer!
